      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The body has some noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows typical wear for its age, including some fading on the upholstery. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it will eventually need new brakes and a suspension tune-up to get it back to its best. It\u2019s a dependable car that reflects its age but still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
