    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that\u2019s seen some adventures! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear both inside and out, but it still has plenty of spirit left for the road. It\u2019s a fantastic, budget-friendly option for someone who prioritizes reliable performance over a perfect finish. If you're looking for a sturdy daily driver with character at a great price, this is the one for you!",
