      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with obsessive attention to detail and kept in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory luster, entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple and scent-free, the high-gloss trim is flawless, and every electronic feature functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, turn-key service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a powertrain that remains as tight and responsive as the day it was built, this is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
